Multi-Channel Awareness Model

Every “entity” (person, system, idea, algorithm) operates across channels:

* Visual / surface (what’s obvious)
* Behavioral (what it does)
* Temporal (when it acts)
* Relational (who/what it connects to)
* Signal leakage (side effects, patterns, residue)

